{"tid":430451,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺開口埋口香港民族好撚嘔心","createTime":"2017-10-09T19:26:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T03:09:49.000Z","uid":54927,"like":30,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1b4f913fa0ee5dcf7d119ec7c17dae61ea2dc271","tid":430451,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T19:26:27.000Z","msg":"呢幾年先有'民族意識' 重要得網上1%人支持既論述<br />\n<br />\n08奧運高登仔就係中華民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n宜家啲死窮撚港豬生活唔好就整一堆19論述出黎要同中國切割又話自己香港民族<br />\n<br />\n我覺得你地為左達到某個目的 就將自己包裝成一個民族呢個字眼去游說所有人係命運共同體呢種功利手段真係好嘔心<br />\n<br />\n唔好講高登唔等於連登<br />\n連登9成人都係高登走過黎<br />\n呢度重多左一堆mk 中小學雞<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯 屌你老母鍵國撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6715b359285547ca644294a7e0ba53facfe90cc3","tid":430451,"uid":54927,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T19:55:21.000Z","msg":"有人話CC台好撚危險 重諗住入黎比狗咬下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n蚊都無隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8424ca8e0429feb1b91e0d7fbfbd2df81906a3a","tid":430451,"uid":54927,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T19:55:41.000Z","msg":"快啲擺我入5毛list 啦"},{"pid":"ab8bc511ab8d2d475eb508a5c46815a05439b5b2","tid":430451,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T19:56:37.000Z","msg":"喂屌你老母快啲用空泛既語言黎回應我啦<br />\n喂港共黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790c995529761393923094ec080116eb2019411d","tid":430451,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T19:56:55.000Z","msg":"喂鍵國撚屌你老母"},{"pid":"a03755d9a3f124f62bd5ce15affb2b7f71dbd330","tid":430451,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T05:07:14.000Z","msg":"?"},{"pid":"acf507e48c4a1085bee3c112e13d822420a7d0dd","tid":430451,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":